      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must be documented with sufficient fidelity to reproduce boundary conditions in the CFD model at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions (flow rates 2.5–7.5 L/min, speeds 2000–3500 RPM) documented in Hariharan et al. (2011). Inlet/outlet pressures and fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C) reproduced in CFD boundary conditions. Gradation 2 met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
