      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison between CFD predictions and experimental measurements of hemolysis index must be performed with documented metrics at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) and relative hemolysis (RH) compared across all 5 operating points. Mean absolute error 8.4%, RH < 1 for all worst-case conditions. Statistical comparison with inter-laboratory experimental variability included. Gradation 3 achieved, exceeding MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
