      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump — a widely accepted surrogate for Class II CPB devices. Operating envelope (flow, speed, fluid) overlaps COU conditions. Geometric similarity confirmed by impeller diameter ratio within 12%. Gradation 2 met."
    },
